            Industrial centrifuges continuously process large volumes of wastewater &mdash; separating sludge, oils, and fine suspended solids from municipal, industrial, mining, and food-processing streams. From sludge dewatering decanters to high-speed disc-stack clarifiers, Dolphin Centrifuge stocks and supplies the right wastewater centrifuge for every application.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
