          <a href="#sludge-thickening" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:underline py-1">Sludge Thickening / Dewatering</a>
          <a href="#mining-effluent" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:underline py-1">Clarifying Centrifuge for Mining Effluent</a>
          <a href="#oily-wastewater" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:underline py-1">Industrial Oily Wastewater Separator</a>
          <a href="#benefits" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:underline py-1">Benefits of Centrifuges</a>
          <a href="#specifications" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:underline py-1">Specifications and Sizing</a>
          <a href="#applications" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:underline py-1">Real-World Applications</a>
          <a href="#models-for-sale" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:underline py-1">Wastewater Centrifuge Models for Sale</a>
          <a href="#faq" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:underline py-1">Frequently Asked Questions</a>
        </nav>
